# Add tests for retry metadata, cleanup semantics, and history insertion only after successful processing

## Requirements

- Add tests for failure bookkeeping and cleanup, not only the successful replay path.
- Verify queue rows do not leak into chat history before successful processing.
- Lock down reset semantics so later refactors do not reintroduce surprise replay behavior.

## Acceptance Criteria

- Tests prove retry metadata updates when replay fails.
- Tests prove reset and low-level cleanup remove pending queue rows.
- Tests prove queued inbound rows become chat history only after successful processing.
